Description: Educational portal app for IT competency development
 An interactive educational portal integrated into the Schulstick platform,
 designed to facilitate IT competency through interactive learning with
 complex computer programs. Features include:
 .
  * Centralized access to curated OER learning materials
  * Interactive step-by-step tutorials
  * Integration with running applications
  * Multi-language support (German/English)
